bhangraa paale paale
ho bhangraa paale paaleteri yeh adaayen teri yeh nigaahen
hosh-awaas udaaye
tere lashkaare karke ishaare
jaana mujhe paas bulaaye
teri zulfon pe teri nazron pe
main toh mar mar jaava
tere pehlu mein tere daaman mein chain-o-sukun main paava
teri baaton ne yaad kiya hai maine dil tujhe dil de diya hai
kaise main tujhe samjhaaun tune kaisa mera haal kiya hai
ho mere sang nain ladale
ho meri zindadi tu bana le
