bhangraa paale paale
ho bhangraa paale paalemaine tujhe dekha maine tujhe chaha
tune mera chain churaya
tere chehre ko tere armaan ko
dhadkan vich hai basaya
o diljana tera main deewana tujhse hai bas yahi kehna
baahon mein chhupa le seene se laga le
tere bin ab nahi rehna
aashiq nahi koi tere jaisa
jaane toh dilbar naiyyo jaani
teri masti mein duba jaaye
gal dil meri gal naiyyo maane
